  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 3f100c39ea54d1945a1f135cd657088f, type: 3}
  m_Name: chap3_3
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::LevelStoryData
  levelName: 
  introLines:
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "T\xF4i mu\u1ED1n n\u1ED5 s\u1EADp c\u1EA3 hang \u0111\u1ED9ng kia \u0111\u1EC3
      l\u1EA5p khe n\u1EE9t \u0111\xF3 l\u1EA1i\u2026"
  - speaker: Dr.Elias
    text: "C\u1EADu b\u1ECB \u0111i\xEAn r\u1ED3i \xE0, \u0110\u1EC3 l\xE0m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
      \u0111i\u1EC1u \u0111\xF3 v\u1EDBi t\xECnh tr\u1EA1ng hi\u1EC7n t\u1EA1i l\xE0
      ho\xE0n to\xE0n kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3. N\u1EBFu kh\xF4ng c\u1EA9n th\u1EADn th\xEC
      c\xF3 th\u1EC3 n\u1ED5 ch\u1EBFt c\u1EA3 \u0111\xE1m tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi cho
      s\u1EADp c\xE1i hang ch\u1EBFt ti\u1EC7t \u0111\xF3 \u0111\u1EA5y. ch\u01B0a
      k\u1EC3 vi\u1EC7c \u0111\u01B0a \u0111\u1ED1ng v\u1EADt n\u1ED5 \u0111\xF3
      \u0111\u1EBFn hang l\xE0 \u0111\xE3 nguy hi\u1EC3m l\u1EAFm r\u1ED3i"
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "T\xF4i tin t\xF4i c\xF3 th\u1EC3 l\xE0m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c , t\xF4i mu\u1ED1n
      k\u1EBFt th\xFAc c\xE1i chuy\u1EC7n ch\u1EBFt ti\u1EC7c \u0111ang x\u1EA3y
      ra l\u1EAFm r\u1ED3i, t\xF4i mu\u1ED1n ng\xF4i nh\xE0 x\u01B0a c\u1EE7a t\xF4i
      v\u1EABn tr\xE0n ng\u1EADp ti\u1EBFng c\u01B0\u1EDDi n\xF3i n\u1EEFa\u2026"
  - speaker: Dr.Elias
    text: "T\xF4i hi\u1EC3u nh\u01B0ng c\u1EADu c\u1EA7n suy ngh\u0129 l\u1EA1i kh\xF4ng
      \u0111i\u1EC1u n\xE0y r\u1EA5t nguy hi\u1EC3m \u0111\u1EA5y!"
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "T\xF4i suy ngh\u0129 k\u0129 r\u1ED3i , t\xF4i mu\u1ED1n b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7
      nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi xung quanh t\xF4i , Shadow , lena\u2026"
  - speaker: Lena
    text: "*H\u1ED9c H\u1ED9c* Aria   b\u1ECDn ch\xFAng l\u1EA1i t\u1EDBi n\u1EEFa
      r\u1ED3i !!"
  outroLines:
  - speaker: Dr.Elias
    text: "\u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c r\u1ED3i t\xF4i hi\u1EC3u r\u1ED3i t\xF4i s\u1EBD
      kh\xF4ng c\u1EA3n c\u1EADu n\u1EEFa , t\xF4i s\u1EBD h\u1ED7 tr\u1EE3 cho c\u1EADu"
